  ;; oracle 0 fail / 400 for distance and isWithinDistance. nearestPoints stays
  ;; quarantined: it returns a Coordinate[], and the port's result-return path
  ;; (_writeWKB / _coordArrayXys) is dim-2, so the Z of the nearest points is
